## Push Summary — skrptiq-cli (main)

### What shipped
Workflow input collection before execution. When a workflow has required input variables (e.g. content, topic), the CLI now:

1. Shows the plan steps
2. Lists required inputs with labels, descriptions, and examples from the plan metadata
3. Prompts for each input sequentially — user types the value and presses enter
4. Once all inputs collected, starts execution with the full input map

If no inputs are required, execution starts immediately.

